pr_body:
This is a reroll of #110 with added changes

@sekka1: I shortened your commit messages because they were too long (http://tbaggery.com/2008/04/19/a-note-about-git-commit-messages.html)

I also used `ubuntu:14.04` as the base image because it makes more sense to automatically switch to  `ubuntu:14.04.5`, `ubuntu:14.04.6`, `ubuntu:14.04.7` as they go out to me. I can remove it if it's a problem.

Instead of having to specify it everywhere, set it on
the Service subclass in cliquet module.

@Natim r?

Possible to add a custom iconCreateFunction to the constructor.

Please see the example below :
icon_create_function = """
function (cluster) {
    var childCount = cluster.getChildCount();
    var c = ' marker-cluster-small';
    return new L.DivIcon({ html: '<div><span>' + childCount + '</span></div>', className: 'marker-cluster' + c, iconSize: new L.Point(40, 40) });
}
"""

@QCoDeS/core 

Handles most issues found by mypy in strict optional mode which is now the default (from 0.600)

Still need to fix an issue with paramter.get/set signature but this can be merged without that
